{"tid":2292304,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"青年藏雷射筆噴漆罪成 還柙至下月初判刑","createTime":"2020-11-19T11:30:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T11:54:27.000Z","uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dade8668c4b49dd268cf8d30b23215bb0a229806","tid":2292304,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T11:30:37.000Z","msg":"裁判官梁少玲今午裁決指，控方兩名警察證人作供清晰確實，沒有誇大、剪裁或動搖，拘捕被告的警員20938亦能講述警車數目等現場細節，全盤接納兩人證供。反之，被告出庭自辯的說法有多處不合理，法庭拒絕接納。<br />\n<br />\n梁官指出，被告稱因7.21事件，故攜帶由上班朋友送贈的鐵碟。惟梁官看過照片後，認為根本就是自制盾牌，但案發時是10月，地點亦非在元朗區，被告的說法不能成理。而案發當日有人號召「區區開花」，被告稱沒看新聞及沒留意通訊群組訊息；惟他在8月曾參加太空館外聲援因購買雷射筆而被捕的人，並承認知道活動目的，故他稱案發當天不知道有社會事件，實在是難以置信。"},{"pid":"a2bd386fa2c75a8694826174833246c21909d09d","tid":2292304,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T11:30:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201119/TYLI373NNZHXFDQUOT67RHEEBQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201119%2FTYLI373NNZHXFDQUOT67RHEEBQ%2F&d=kK8wO%2BHHGyY98lbbYtfopZugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=2c5b66be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201119%2FTYLI373NNZHXFDQUOT67RHEEBQ%2F&h=35d9327a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201119/TYLI373NNZHXFDQUOT67RHEEBQ/</a>"},{"pid":"2912fa4f893b0b80d84c1ab5f2d25a9412d1fddc","tid":2292304,"uid":301050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T11:33:37.000Z","msg":"自制盾牌...<br />\n咁點???當佢美國隊長?擲盾?"},{"pid":"03b00caabb7187952e449199d8e4bca3e337e66d","tid":2292304,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T11:38:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3026075a5fbd1d7e234176dfff1ef12360d7d75","tid":2292304,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"sc